	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="#regest1">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">De charta, quę primo venit in manus, ne cures, postquam festinandum fuit.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div2" corresp="#regest2">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex evangelicis<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Zu verstehen: Ex evangelicis Helveticorum.</note> sunt, qui vires omnes sunt addicturi civitatibus imperii, quicquid dicant Quinquepagici.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu fac idem tuis persuadeas.<pb type="edition" next="363"/></s>
				</ab>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div3" corresp="#regest3">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exercitus, quicquid Hessi custodierint, Rhenum transiit apud oppidum <placeName ref="139">Bingen</placeName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Zur Rheinüberquerung der von Maximilian von Egmont, Graf von Büren, angeführten Truppen s. <ref target="files.xml#12595">Nr. 2548</ref>, Anm. 50.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid nunc sit facturus, nescio.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div4" corresp="#regest4">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Per Sungoviam et Alsatiam tumultuatur, quamobrem, ignoratur.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">In primis ad Ensheim munitiones instituuntur roboribus quercinis<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Zu den Kriegsvorbereitungen im <placeName ref="85">Sundgau</placeName> und im <placeName ref="16">Elsass</placeName> (u.a. in <placeName ref="323">Ensisheim</placeName>) s. schon <persName ref="154">Myconius</persName>' Mitteilungen in <ref target="files.xml#12587">Nr. 2540</ref>,19-24.</note>.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div5" corresp="#regest5">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cęsarem<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Karl V. war am 15. August aus <placeName ref="594">Landshut</placeName> abgereist und lag vom 17. bis 21. August vor <placeName ref="880">Regensburg</placeName>; s. <ref target="files.xml#12588">Nr. 2541</ref>, Anm. 29. Von dort aus zog er nicht in Richtung <placeName ref="839">Passau</placeName>, sondern nach <placeName ref="1591">Neustadt</placeName> ad. Donau und <placeName ref="513">Ingolstadt</placeName> weiter; s. <ref target="files.xml#12598">Nr. 2551</ref>, Anm. 13; <ref target="files.xml#12608">Nr. 2561</ref>,6-9.</note> aiunt reliquisse <placeName ref="26">Landshuͦtum</placeName>, rediisse <placeName ref="880">Ratisponam</placeName>, nec ibi mansurum, sed <placeName ref="839">Patavium</placeName> abiturum.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mihi videtur in animo habere, ut pios Germanos delasset ac pecunia evacuet, ut in annum sequentem securius nos adgrediatur.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dico tibi, vir astu et malicia belligeratur contra dei homines!</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div6" corresp="#regest6">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="121">Helvetiorum</placeName> ex omnibus pagis video esse paratos contra Carolum innumeros.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Transeunt hac Tigurini, <placeName ref="121">Bernenses</placeName>, <placeName ref="136">Bielenses</placeName>, <placeName ref="243">Curienses</placeName>, <placeName ref="652">Lucernani</placeName>, <placeName ref="1238">Tugini</placeName> vehementer alacres<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Zu den eidgenössischen Söldnern s. <ref target="files.xml#12595">Nr. 2548</ref>, Anm. 40; <hi><persName ref="74">Gast</persName>, Tagebuch</hi> 288f (unter dem 26. August); <hi>PC</hi> IV/1 351, <ref target="files.xml#10365">Nr. 333</ref>.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic mihi dolet, quod multi coguntur redire domum, quia pecunia deest.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et putant exteri, quod propriis sumptibus deberemus mittere exercitum iustum, ignorantes morem nostrum<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Gemeint ist das Reislaufen.</note>, ad quem sumus adsueti, dum procul abimus, iam longo tempore.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nescio, quid inde possit tandem fieri.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div7" corresp="#regest7">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hunc tibi commendo, qui literas fert, ut doctum<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Francisco de Enzinas; s. <ref target="files.xml#12601">Nr. 2554</ref>.</note> valde.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale cum tuis.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="97">Basileę</placeName>, 27. augusti anno 1546.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div8" corresp="#regest8">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Os. <persName ref="154">Myconius</persName> tuus.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. Heinricho Bullingero, in domino suo.</s>
					<s xml:lang="de" type="auto">Z[urich]<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>Textverlust durch Entfernung des Siegels.</hi></note>.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
